        <updateDate>2014-05-09T12:36:32Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Servicemembers Opportunity Act - Amends the Servicemembers Civil Relief Act to allow any appropriate indicator of military service, including a certified letter from a commanding officer or information from the Defense Manpower Database Center, as proof of service for purposes of interest rate limitations provided to servicemembers under such Act.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
